Brasil - São Paulo - São Paulo
Instituto de Metemática e Estatística da Universidade de São Paulo (IME - USP)
C++, CUDA and OpenCL implementations of Runge-Kutta methods (orders 2 and 4) applied to vector fields

################
# Introduction #
################

The first prototype can be found on https://github.com/rafamanzo/runge-kutta. This new prototype has a similar architeture, but uses the VTK library instead of directly OpenGL.

